				</div>
				<div>
					<img src="/logo/xSens.webp" alt="xSens" class="h-12 w-12 object-contain mx-auto mb-2" />
					<p class="text-white">xSens Mocap</p>
				</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>
		<section id="about" aria-label="About" class="bg-[#0B1120] py-14 pb-20">
			<div class="px-4 md:px-12 lg:px-20 mx-auto max-w-screen-xl">
				<h2 class="text-center text-5xl font-extrabold mb-10">About Me üôã‚Äç‚ôÇÔ∏è</h2>
				<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center text-white">
				<p class="text-lg text-gray-300 mb-6">
					I'm a character rigger and technical artist with professional experience working in Madrid, Spain and Edinburgh, Scotland. I enjoy solving complex problems and developing custom rigs and tools to streamline workflows and support efficient production.
				</p>
					<p>Connect with me on 
						<a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/andrewsupertramp/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-block text-blue-400 hover:text-blue-300 transition text-lg font-medium">
						LinkedIn</a>
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>
	</div>
	
	<main>
		
